|---------------------------------|
| VIFM                            |
|---------------------------------|
|---------------------------------|
| Moves                           |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| to the first file               |          H |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| to the mimddle file             |          M |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| to the last file                |          L |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| toggles between file lists      |      space |
|---------------------------------+------------|
|---------------------------------|
| Pane manipulation (C-W)         |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| move pane to far left           |          H |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| move pane to very bottom        |          J |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| move pane to very top           |          K |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| move pane to far right          |          L |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to bottom-right          |          b |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to left                  |          h |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to pane below            |          j |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to pane above            |          k |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to right pane            |          l |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| only                            |          o |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to previous              |          p |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| split                           |          s |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to top-left              |          t |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| vsplit                          |          v |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch to other pane            |          w |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| exchange panes                  |          x |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| maximize current view           |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| make sizes equal                |          = |
|---------------------------------+------------|
|---------------------------------|
| File filters                    |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| show dot files                  |         zo |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| fitler all of selected files    |         zf |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| toggle dot files                |         za |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| show filtered by file name      |         zO |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| filter matching file name       |         zM |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| remove all filters              |         zR |
|---------------------------------+------------|
|-+-|
|---------------------------------|
| Other usefull commands          |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| go backward                     |        C-O |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| go forward                      |        C-I |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| info about current file         |        C-G |
|---------------------------------+-------+----|
| enters view mode (when view     |  Shift+Tab |
| enabled)                        |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| calculate directory size        |         ga |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| like ga, force update           |         gA |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| find link destination           |         gf |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| go to visual mode, restoring    |         gv |
| last selection                  |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| restore last t selection        |         gs |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| make names of selected          |         gu |
| - lowercase                     |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| make names - uppercase          |         gU |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| explore file in current pane    |          e |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open file with associated app   |          i |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| rename file or files            |         cw |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change only name of file        |         cW |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change link target              |         cl |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change file owner               |         co |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change file group               |         cg |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change file attributes          |         cp |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| clone file [count] times        |   [count]C |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| move selected to trash          |         dd |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| remove selected                 |         DD |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| yank selected                   |       yy,Y |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| copy yanked files               |       pp,P |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| put symbolic links with         |         al |
| absolut path                    |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| put with relative paths         |         rl |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| select or unselect              |          t |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| undo last change                |          u |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| redo last change                |        C-R |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| enter visual mode               |        v,V |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| increment first number in file  | [count]C-A |
| name by count                   |            |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| decrement                       | [count]C-X |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| quit                            |         ZZ |
|---------------------------------+------------|
|-+-|
|---------------------------------|
| Visual Mode                     |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| save selection and go to normal |      Enter |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| restore previous selection      |         gv |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| leave visual mode               |        v,V |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| switch active selection bound   |        o,O |
|---------------------------------+------------|
|-+-|
|---------------------------------|
| Mappings                        |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open shell                      |          s |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| change sort mode                |          S |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open view pane                  |          w |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open in gvim                    |        o,O |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open file in bg                 |         gb |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| yank current directory          |         yd |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| yank current file path          |         yf |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| rename in beginning             |          I |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| rename full                     |         cc |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| rename only name                |          A |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| open vifmrc                     |         ,c |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| chreate tar archive             |        C-p |
|---------------------------------+------------|
| untar archive                   |      Alt-u |
